children.description:
**Benchmark file for ThunderKittens rotary embeddings on modern GPUs**

Analyze Kernels: 3-1-1024/2048/4096/8192

* Optimizes rotary attention kernels using FlashAttention's fused rotaries on H100;
* Runs comprehensive BLAS-benchmark-style go/no-go tests across different sequence lengths;
* Compares TFLOPS per operation using a reference PyTorch benchmark for every k-size;
* Actively tests TK 8192 optimization (integer pipeline + non-integer matrix multiplies + asynchronous loads) to avoid memory pressure;
* Measures kernel latency, not just FLOPs (important for Rocktensors specifically).
